{"tid":1383593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無諗過超合作運動？","createTime":"2019-07-29T17:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T17:42:31.000Z","uid":61219,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de4e1dbc52a1827b956900da142598cc65e770bc","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"頭先同父母傾計 講起林鄭話自己係啊媽 不如試下用啊仔lur啊媽既方法 煩到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家政府唔肯俾我地遊行 要我地集會 <br />\n我地不如就聽佢講 每個星期六去啲細既場玩 「按章集會」<br />\n例如去修頓球場 遮打花園 甚至元朗大球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我假設有15萬人出黎 正常黎講 我地應該會企埋出馬路 <br />\n但係如果我地唔好企出馬路 而係企係行人路呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時啲遊客馬路又過唔到 附近商舖又無得開 咪變相做到癱瘓既作用 <br />\n然後走個陣15萬人一齊走 交通都塞爆你 何其震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而勇武既巴打就可以回下氣 一齊屌下狗<br />\n<br />\n佢地又無得打鳩我地 谷住谷住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：奉公守法良好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b2a450b314a79ea5c943e110ed9a14d77628ab","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"99bcf4dbd61927db8b2d566e1ad5978484832d0f","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"58b3d9f9b0d035fad94debf0d014fbd0950802bc","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4360b4070d26cc2def109187e28819a4b56df9ff","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:22:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"38d437916841a6507a640900c33590c731a46354","tid":1383593,"uid":61219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4ffa1